RDP to \\hamfs (or fileserver of remote)
Go to Users folder of fileserver
Create folder with user's first initial and last name

Permissions:
Disable inheritance
Domain users needed: user, domain admins, workstation admins
user receives modify permission, both admins receive full control
Sharing tab > Advanced sharing > Share this folder, append "$" to name of folder
Permissions: user, domain admins, workstation admins; each with same respective permissions as before

Look at another folder to check on whether or not these settings match
